              ],
              "Enabled": true,
              "ReadOnly": false
            },
            {
              "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
              "Text": "#Future Development requirements\n\n* Phenology not responding to stress events.  Requires better data sets for quantifying the effects of water and nitrogen on leaf apperance and the timing of development stages.\n* Phosphorus response\n* Improved parameterisation of supply and demand for N and DM from organs and arbitration of these resources.\n* Heat Stress responses in grain number\n* More validation under a wider range of environments with more detailed datasets\n* Seedling mortality\n* Water demand (MicroClimate) needs validation\n\n\n\n\n",
              "Name": "Future Development Needs",
              "ResourceName": null,
              "Children": [],
              "Enabled": true,
              "ReadOnly": false
            },
